commitResults.messageTitle: Level-1: Implemented with while-loop and Scanner class
Level-2: Implemented nested condition in while-loop
Level-3: Implemented A-Class for Commands
Level-4: ToDos, Deadlines, Events. Implemented with A-Inheritance.
A_TextUiTesting: Added automatic testing, corrected line spacing.
Level-6: Changed HashMap<Integer, Task> to Arraylist<Task> to support delete function. Updated autotesting to validate delete function.
Level-7: - Added file output stream to save updated tasks to tasks.json (Duke.java) - implemented Serializable class (Task.java)
Level-7: Save * load serialized tasks to tasks.txt before exiting Duke (TaskList.java) * refactored code to shorter methods (Duke.java)
Level-8 Date: * takes in deadline date in ISO_LOCAL_DATE format and prints in d-MMM-yyyy format

A-More-OOP: * Added Parser class to parse through commands (Parser.java) * Added abstract Command class to initialise Task objects and perform commands based on Command::execute 	* Added ListCommand, ExitCommand, DeleteCommand, MarkCommand, UnmarkCommand, TodoCommand, DeadlineCommand, EventCommand * Added Ui class to read user input and produce output (confirmation and error messages)
A-Packages: * created duke package * organised classes into tasks, parser, commands, exception, ui, and storage packages
A-JUnit: * added JUnit test classes to test: 	* Todo object instantiation 	* DeadlineCommand Deadline object instantiation
A-JavaDocs: * added JavaDocs to all files * TODO: @docRoot

Level-9: * added FindCommand class to execute the task finding * added a COMMAND_FIND constant to Parser to parse out a FindCommand object * added a KeywordFinder interface to implement a method to find tasks with the keyword

A-CodingStandard: * adjusted boolean variable names to sound like booleans * adjusted long method arguments to fit max length * adjusted whitespacing between math operators * renamed class fields to be more consistent * removed indent for switch statement * removed wildcard import in Storage class
no message
A-Checkstyle: * corrected code quality according to Gradle Checkstyle
A-UserGuide: * Edited program outputs to be more consistent * Edited User Guide
Implemented GUI: * Added JavaFX GUI * Added User and Duke profile image
Add Ui prototype * Added Ui.png * Edited find command program output (line breaks between task elements)
